filters.whereClause: clcommon__Collateral__c IN :Mapping__Collaterals__CollateralId  ORDER BY clcommon__Appraisal_Date__c DESC
clcommon__Collateral__c IN :Mapping__Collaterals__CollateralId AND genesis__Application__c = :applicationId AND clcommon__Status__c = 'Proposed'

clcommon__Collateral__c IN :Mapping__Collaterals__CollateralId AND genesis__Application__c != :applicationId AND clcommon__Collateral__r.clcommon__Collateral_Type__r.clcommon__Collateral_Type_Code__c = 'Investment Property'

Id IN :Mapping__Parties__AccountId OR Id IN :Mapping__Parties__ContactAccountId OR Id IN :Mapping__Relationships__Entity OR Id in :Mapping__ApplicationLevel__Auto_Debit_Account_OwnerId OR Id in :Mapping__ApplicationLevel__SettlementAgentId OR Id in :Mapping__ApplicationLevel__SettlementAgentContactId OR Id in :Mapping__Collaterals__LifeInsuranceBeneficiary OR Id in :Mapping__Collaterals__ControllingInstitution OR Id in :Mapping__Collaterals__InsuredParty OR Id in :Mapping__Collaterals__InsuranceCompanyId OR Id in :Mapping__Collaterals__landlordOfTheLeasedProperty OR Id in :Mapping__CollateralOwners__accountId
ints__CreditReport__r.genesis__Applications__c = :applicationId AND ints__CreditReport__r.ints__Contact__c IN :Mapping__Contacts__Id ORDER BY CreatedDate DESC
ints__CreditReportScore__c in :Mapping__CreditReportScore__Id ORDER BY CreatedDate DESC
